headline: Billionaire Bill Ackman May Be the Next Warren Buffett. He's Buying 2 Magnificent Stocks Up 160% and 270% Since 2023.
summary: Hedge fund billionaire Bill Ackman hopes to recreate Warren Buffett's success by turning Howard Hughes into a "modern-day Berkshire Hathaway."  Ackman's hedge fund took a stake in Amazon in the second quarter, betting on the resilience of its retail and cloud computing businesses.  Ackman's hedge fund took a stake in Uber in the first quarter, saying it is "one of the best managed and highest quality businesses in the world."
